      • test_datatype_ordering

        public void test_datatype_ordering()
        Unit test verifies the order imposed across the different datatypes (but not within those datatypes).

        Note: openrdf imposes the following type precedence: 

                      - simple literal
              - numeric
              - xsd:boolean
              - xsd:dateTime
              - xsd:string
              - RDF term (equal and unequal only)
